    "title": "Hiring Store Manager at Borosil",
    "description": "Borosil is actively seeking a talented and motivated Store Manager to join our dynamic team in Indore. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Borosil:\nBorosil is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Borosil!",
